      "content": "wait u said research \"consistently shows\" they fail. but what about the argument that strict sentencing actually deters people from committing crimes in the first place? like if the punishment is certain and severe, doesn't that discourage crime? i feel like u're kind of dismissing that whole side of the debate.",
